Title: Stockfighter
Description:
Stockfighter is a series of puzzles which you'll solve by programming. Each builds on the last, teaching you more about the problem domain and letting you strut your stuff a bit.

Stockfighter is organized into tech trees, which are a series of levels which build on each other in terms of both the technology you'll use and the concepts you'll learn. You can play either of our tech trees at the left.
